text: Leif Johan Korn (born 26 July 1937) is a retired Swedish gymnast. He competed in all gymnastics events at the 1960 and the 1964 Summer Olympics with the best result of ninth place on the rings in 1964. ==References== Korn in 1960 * Category:1937 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Sweden Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Stockholm
